{"tid":878263,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"D大陸佬飛象過河真係唔屌唔得","createTime":"2018-10-27T03:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T08:36:42.000Z","uid":175329,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60c2c50f70b059cf1c2ddd93fdc93a93661d821e","tid":878263,"uid":175329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"話說我係日本自由行去緊四萬十川，坐緊火車而家，有條大陸仔見架火車冇物人就飛象過河，點解我知佢係大陸人？因為佢拎住簡體版四國旅遊書. 咁我就同佢講：Could you please lay down your legs on the seat? This is a rude behaviour. （英文有錯請屌）<br />\n<br />\n條友唔知真唔明定假唔明，咁我就用普通話叫佢放低隻腳. 佢終於有d老尷話唔知唔可以放腳上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話有d行為真係唔屌唔得，重要係日本. <br />\n<br />\n話之前同講左之後<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/114432_4e8df923cdedcd0a9fe773c5c3ed2c9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F114432_4e8df923cdedcd0a9fe773c5c3ed2c9f.png&h=02bc9337&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/114454_e8b99ab874d7ae5f452add9161fdfb55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F114454_e8b99ab874d7ae5f452add9161fdfb55.png&h=ee855da6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c08c45439112e2de81fc2ed32f92d5ba976532f7","tid":878263,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"去踩單車?<br />\n<br />\n窗出面好似幾好天"},{"pid":"053e8fa34f9381c9d437128142caebc5bb7274da","tid":878263,"uid":175329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c08c45439112e2de81fc2ed32f92d5ba976532f7","tid":878263,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"去踩單車?<br />\n<br />\n窗出面好似幾好天"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"到左會租單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前日去左石鎚山<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/2